categoryInfoList.title: Hotel Star Rating
categoryInfoList.desc: The hotel star rating is provided by third-party organizations or institutions and offers valuable insights into a property's amenities, services, and other relevant aspects.

items.name: 5 Stars (Luxury Hotels)
items.desc: These hotels are comfortable and luxurious, offering a large range of personalised services that enhance the overall stay experience.

items.name: 4 Stars (Upscale Hotels)
items.desc: With high standards for service and amenities, these hotels feature offerings catered to business travellers and holidaymakers alike.

items.name: 3 Stars (Mid-range Hotels)
items.desc: These hotels go a step beyond the basics with more space, amenities, and a comfortable environment.

items.name: 2 Stars (Economy Hotels)
items.desc: Hotels have facilities and some fundamental services that satisfy general needs. The overall environment is neat and clean.

items.name: 1 Star (Budget Hotels)
items.desc: With clean and comfortable rooms, these hotels are budget-friendly and simple.

categoryInfoList.title: Homestay Rating
categoryInfoList.desc: The homestay rating provides a thorough assessment of amenities, services and other relevant aspects.

items.name: Level 5 (Luxury Homestays)
items.desc: The epitome of style and comfort. Look forward to an expansive layout, lavish furnishings, and exceptional amenities.

items.name: Level 4 (Upscale Homestays)
items.desc: Upscale properties for more luxurious stays. Rooms are stylish and roomy with a well-defined living space and well-appointed bathrooms.

items.name: Level 3 (Mid-range Homestays)
items.desc: These properties meet travellers' basic needs and then some. Expect clean, comfortable rooms with private bathrooms and simple amenities.

items.name: Level 2 (Economy Homestays)
items.desc: Accommodation for those who prioritize affordability over luxury. Think modest rooms, simple decor, and limited amenities. Bathrooms may be shared.

items.name: Level 1 (Budget Homestays)
items.desc: No-frills accommodation for travellers on a budget. Rooms have limited space and are equipped only with the essentials. Bathrooms may be shared.
